extracted_text: 3.13.03. Density: One mobile home per pad or one manufactured home per lot. No more than eight mobile homes are permitted per acre of land.
llm_output.rationale: The section titled 'Sec. 3.13. - MH Mobile home-manufactured housing district' provides the density regulation which is closely related to the floor_to_area_ratio as it determines the number of dwelling units per acre of land.
